<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Week of the Baby - Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: #eef2f3;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
